リラックスできる美しいパズルゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 點點相連，攜手探索新世界
動腦連線 暢快消除同色點點

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A minimalist puzzler through and through, TwoDots—the single-player sequel to Dots—delivers accessible and satisfying challenges by the bucketful. While its style and sound mirror the unvarnished nature of its puzzles, its seemingly simple exterior hides a compelling depth that’ll keep you coming back for more.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Make a square, how hard is that? Spoiler alert, it is.
